      <section id="section_ed4_zpv_pzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Purpose</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To define a work instruction for the inspection of portable and fixed ladders on a
            semi-annual basis.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">On a semi-annual basis all ladders (portable and fixed) shall be inspected by a
            qualified person, ladder user, or designated/authorized person.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="section_xsx_1qv_pzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Application</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">This procedure applies to all Space employees, contractors and visitors, and all
            operations including manufacturing facilities, laboratories, R&amp;D facilities,
            technical centers, offices, and administrative buildings where ladders and portable
            stairs are used.</p>
      </section>
